<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199648>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Eulimnadia azisi sp. nov. (female) (A – H) A. Carapace growth lines, B. Head, C. First antenna with sensory lobes, D. Second Antenna (lateral view), E. First thoracopod (typical), F. Telson with unequal dorsal spines, G. Telson (posterior portion enlarged), H. Egg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

